item.title: Apache HTTP server (httpd)
item.description: The Apache HTTP Server is a free and open-source cross-platform web server software, released under the terms of Apache License 2.0.

item.title: Nginx
item.description: Nginx (pronounced “engine x” /ˌɛndʒɪnˈɛks/ EN-jin-EKS, stylized as NGINX) is a web server that can also be used as a reverse proxy, load balancer, mail proxy and HTTP cache.
